{"tid":603292,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"國際巨商 Great Merchant 港人美服討論區 (8)","createTime":"2018-03-23T15:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T15:35:21.000Z","uid":81742,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e8870411fbc2fc12e192d8e933e9d937b2acaf50","tid":603292,"uid":81742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T15:23:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/pGYAnUT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpGYAnUT.png&h=54bb07f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巨商都十年以上, 相信各位應該聽過依隻game. 隻遊戲都經營左一段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遊戲畫面同戰鬥系統都算經典, 十年間界面改變唔大, 依家多左唔同傭兵將領神獸天王凶獸<br />\n四天王：虎天（左上）龍天（右上）雀天（左下）龜天（右下）<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/UCmeyJg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUCmeyJg.png&h=41e6c954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無人踏足既蒙古地區<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/j90LfdD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj90LfdD.png&h=88652fe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劇情模式<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HkKGIsw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHkKGIsw.png&h=c6f5906f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度地區<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/xCvZGPa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxCvZGPa.png&h=74db441c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩巨商既玩家分兩種: 戰商同大商人<br />\n前者就主要玩打怪打寶打Boss 賺錢, 屬於實戰型<br />\n後者就係靠唔同方法賺錢包括跑商, 匠人, 廠主等等<br />\nRaidcall ID: 26477299 <br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 點解要玩?<br />\nA: 少外掛 物價合理 打寶有市 可無課起家 可三開  英語溝通買賣冇難度<br />\n<br />\nQ: 係邊度下載遊戲 ?<br />\nA: <a href=\"http://可以係官網www.thegreatmerchant.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BF%82%E5%AE%98%E7%B6%B2www.thegreatmerchant.com&d=9qwVmVD3aCsyYotQX9g%2BG9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=3e44d6b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">可以係官網www.thegreatmerchant.com</a> 下載, 記得申請account 要用hotmail/email, 因為暫時gmail 唔受理<br />\n<br />\nQ: 新手第一次玩可以點起手 ?<br />\nA: 咁要視乎你會唔會課金/喜歡白手興家, 前者輕鬆賺一桶金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後者都有唔同玩法, 比如揀國籍已經有差別, 選擇邊幾隻將帥等等. 詳情可以問人 同埋不定時有人帶升~<br />\n<br />\nQ: 遊戲多唔多人玩 ?<br />\nA: 暫時美服人數岩岩好, 有一班香港人玩 同時有印尼 內地 台灣 日本 韓國人玩...<br />\n<br />\nQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />isconnected to server 點算?<br />\nA:一次半次好正常，如果經常發生可能關防火牆／防毒事<br />\n<br />\n諗住咁多先, 有問題再加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">樓主警告: 外掛狗死全家</span><br />\n<br />\nRaidCall 官網下載<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.raidcall.com.tw/download.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.raidcall.com.tw%2Fdownload.php&d=9qwVmVD3aCsyYotQX9g%2BG9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=5eb3813e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.raidcall.com.tw/download.php</a><br />\n<br />\n巨商遊戲下載<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thegreatmerchant.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thegreatmerchant.com%2F&d=9qwVmVD3aCsyYotQX9g%2BG9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=5ebb38be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thegreatmerchant.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n大陸52巨商攻略<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.52jushang.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.52jushang.com%2F&d=9qwVmVD3aCsyYotQX9g%2BG9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=a817fc08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.52jushang.com/</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5267a663df741fd4c2fe3e706c6b8e949bf35605","tid":603292,"uid":81742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T17:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc020439de3a36b4ffcc68bb33ebf9d17bd985e","tid":603292,"uid":81742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T03:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58d431ecd8af3982ce2